OL,4,CEveryone's Invited: Schools abuse
OL,5,Chelpline and review launched
OL,6, A helpline and immediate review into
OL,7, sexual abuse in schools have been set
OL,8, up by the government in response to
OL,9, thousands of allegations from students.
OL,11,FOfsted will look at safeguarding in
OL,12,Fboth state and independent schools.
OL,14,FThe helpline will be run by the NSPCC
OL,15,Fto both support potential victims and
OL,16,Fprovide advice to children and adults.
OL,18,F"Sexual abuse in any form is abhorrent
OL,19,Fand it is vital that these allegations
OL,20,Fare dealt with properly," Education
OL,21,FSecretary Gavin Williamson said.
